---
title: Japanese-Style Pork Schnitzel with Katsu Sauce & Pear-Radish Slaw
description: Give pork schnitzel a Japanese-inspired twist by serving it with a killer katsu sauce and crisp radish slaw. It's a crowd-pleasing combo that's surprisingly carb smart. Prepare for repeat requests!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
